OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FThe Three Lions have kicked off their
OL,7,Fsecond game of the 2026 Fifa World
OL,8,FCup, playing Ghana at the Gillette
OL,9,FStadium in Boston.
OL,11,FFollowing their opening game victory
OL,12,Fagainst Croatia, another win would
OL,13,Fguarantee England's progression to the
OL,14,Flast 32 in the tournament.
OL,16,FA loss for Panama, who play Croatia
OL,17,Fearly on Wednesday, would secure
OL,18,FEngland's position at the top of the
OL,19,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
