FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782267480
OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FMore than 14,000 fans are thought to
OL,7,Fhave travelled to Boston for the game
OL,8,Fin support of the Three Lions `
OL,9,Fdespite high ticket costs, transport
OL,10,Fprices and parking charges.
OL,12,FTheir opponents, Ghana, are currently
OL,13,F65th in the world, making them
OL,14,FEngland's weakest rivals of the group
OL,15,Fstage in terms of ranking.
OL,17,FThomas Tuchel's side are very much the
OL,18,Ffavourites, but Ghana have a weapon
OL,19,Fthat England know very well, as
OL,20,FManchester City star Antoine Semenyo
OL,21,Fwill provide a big threat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782267480
OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FSemenyo lit up the Premier League
OL,7,Ffollowing his mid-season move to the
OL,8,FEtihad Stadium, and England's defence
OL,9,Fwill have to be on guard to keep the
OL,10,F26-year-old London-born winger quiet.
OL,12,FThe England team are seeking to
OL,13,Freplicate their second-half display
OL,14,Fagainst Croatia in Boston, where
OL,15,Fvictory against Ghana will secure
OL,16,Ftheir place in the next round, with a
OL,17,Fmatch to go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
