OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782267480
OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FEngland would also head into
OL,7,FSaturday's final Group L game against
OL,8,FPanama as pool winners, should the
OL,9,Fcentral American nation fail to beat
OL,10,FCroatia later on Tuesday.
OL,12,FA positive outcome would allow Tuchel
OL,13,Fto rotate and rest star names at
OL,14,FMetLife Stadium, where they hope to
OL,15,Freturn on July 19 for a shot at World
OL,16,FCup glory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
