CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782267480
OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FAfter England played their first match
OL,7,Funder a roof in the air-conditioned
OL,8,FAT&T Stadium in Dallas, their match in
OL,9,Fthe Boston Stadium is their first test
OL,10,Fin the hot and humid conditions.
OL,12,FHowever, looks to be more favourable
OL,13,Fwith cloud, rain and much cooler
OL,14,Ftemperatures.
OL,16,FOn Monday, hundreds of England fans
OL,17,Fwere out in Boston's bars as they
OL,18,Flooked to match Scotland fans'
OL,19,Fdrinking habits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
