OL,3,CEngland vs Ghana World Cup match kicks
OL,4,Coff
OL,6,FBoston hosted the Tartan Army for the
OL,7,Ffirst two games of their World Cup
OL,8,Fcampaign, with several bars being
OL,9,Fdrank dry.
OL,11,FMeet Boston, a tourism organisation in
OL,12,Fthe city, estimated about 50,000
OL,13,FScotland supporters visited for the
OL,14,Fteam's first two matches.
OL,16,FThey said two popular bars ` The
OL,17,FDubliner and The Haven ` reportedly
OL,18,Fserved more than 300 kegs of Tennent's
OL,19,Fbeer between them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
